name: Osuno_Whett
content:
Osuno Whett was a human individual who was depicted in a statue at the University of Bar'leth. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, when Kho Phon Farrus returned to the university, the statue still stood.
Osuno Whett first canonically appeared in the nineteenth issue of the 2020 comic book series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra, written by Alyssa Wong, illustrated by Minkyu Jung, and published by Marvel Comics on March 23, 2022. In the Star Wars Legends continuity, Whett first appeared in Lando Calrissian and the Mindharp of Sharu, a novel written by L. Neil Smith and published in 1983 as the first installment of the Star Wars: The Lando Calrissian Adventures.
